          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ". It does mean the German automaker will just be adapting what it has already to the new standards. Duesmann added that the new requirements from Euro 7 could be “technically huge” while offering “little benefit for the environment.” In other words, he doesn’t seem to be a fan of the changes.",
